  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      30 patients had lacrimal sac mucocele and dacryocystorhinostomy was done for them with
      intraoperative mitomycin C was added to decrease postoperative fibrosis and recurrence.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
